ilog.concert

Interface IloTupleSchema


  • public interface IloTupleSchema
    This class declares an IloTupleSet schema. It defines the type of the columns in the declared IloTupleSet schema.

      • end

        void end()
        This method deletes the invoking implementation. That is, it frees all the resources used by the invoking object. After a call to this method, you cannot use the invoking extractable object again.
